message: You are projecting. Someone not opening a discussion on the talk page does not hinder YOU from doing so. Again they are an alt metal band so their intro should state that. Take the article Total Ntertainment on their latest album Mother (2020) for example. The article does mention different rock influences used in some of the songs on the album. However the very FIRST/OPENING sentence of the article and the LAST paragraph of the article states that their main genre as “alt metal” NOT “rock”....

This edit was made to be consistent with the genre classification of the band made by various reputable music publications, outlets, as well as the band members themselves.

For example, Total Ntertainment published an article on their latest album Mother (2020) which is linked on the page. The article does mention different rock influences used in some of the songs on the album. However the very FIRST/OPENING sentence of the article and the LAST paragraph of the article states that their main genre as “alt metal” NOT “rock”. Reputable music publications obviously understand the significance of this
